#: ../../S/See-figure-1.rst:5
msgid "See figure 1"
msgstr "See figure 1"

#: ../../S/See-figure-1.rst:7
msgid ""
"Metaphorically, \"Get stuffed.\" From the title of a famous parody that can "
"easily be found with a web search on this phrase; figure 1, in fact, depicts"
" the digitus impudicus."
msgstr ""
"比喩的に「失せろ」。このフレーズをWebで検索すれば簡単に見つかる有名なパロディの題名に由来する。図1は、実際にはdigitus "
"impudicus(無礼の指、すなわち中指)を描いている。"
